text:
Strong earthquake rocks New Britain region, Papua New Guinea   
Sep 16, 2015 eTN   
Magnitude 6.0 earthquake struck New Britain region, Papua New Guinea. 
Preliminary Earthquake Report: 
Date-Time • 16 Sep 2015 14:03:22 UTC 
• 17 Sep 2015 00:03:22 near epicenter • 16 Sep 2015 03:03:22 standard time in your timezone Location 6.001S 151.454E Distances • 153 km (94 mi) ESE of Kimbe, Papua New Guinea • 203 km (125 mi) SSW of Kokopo, Papua New Guinea • 385 km (238 mi) S of Kavieng, Papua New Guinea • 452 km (280 mi) W of Arawa, Papua New Guinea • 605 km (375 mi) NE of Port Moresby, Papua New Guinea Location Uncertainty Horizontal: 7.7 km; Vertical 3.5 km Parameters Nph = 105; Dmin = 215.1 km; Rmss = 1.13 seconds; Gp = 20°
